n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234862</a>"},{"pid":"b506086ac23f30ee9bde3e4944535240c704f43c","tid":1235206,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"Suggestion / Strategy 寫出黎有好多種<br />\n<br />\n我唔會要求大家只做一項，反而係取長補短才是致勝之道<br />\n<br />\n我們要令林鄭「終身後悔」<br />\n<br />\n進退有時，勇猛有時<br />\n平淡有時，柔情有時<br />\n<br />\nBe Water Everyone!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0614d129db4a23516c70eb139e71c224a32d115","tid":1235206,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"fc9185c35f86d923641e0b85b2f3a561cd3177e8","tid":1235206,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"【反送中過後】屌你老味!!! 下星期就係《國歌法》二讀嘞....<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPCuyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPCuyS</a>"},{"pid":"706825949a202d738d2238231b704478cb29c982","tid":1235206,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:49:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨裁者往往勝利的原因，就是等待反抗者內部分裂</span>"},{"pid":"42d6957fe849d6a3dba5858563c76ef001353ae8","tid":1235206,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:49:21.000Z","msg":"very good！<br />\n簡而精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f2dc189fe3c74ee7d256eef1c5c2e50dde0397","tid":1235206,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff49407c8be80c420f7a572c1da040a02a6a196f","tid":1235206,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"706825949a202d738d2238231b704478cb29c982","tid":1235206,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:49:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨裁者往往勝利的原因，就是等待反抗者內部分裂</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"同樣我地都要進退有時，堅守原則，因為對家嘅內部分裂問題唔會比我地細"},{"pid":"63de9fb01684545acf61530e729acab3167ade8b","tid":1235206,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"間隔仲話要成立臨時政府建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該睇下第三點"},{"pid":"8954e2dfc12ebeb17c119ee2a75a0e07fa0e956f","tid":1235206,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:52:51.000Z","msg":"文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f2f067cdaa3cca03a137ef407aef2f5d211aea","tid":1235206,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3eba23632847105cb9c8eabf8ae1cf3747c6f6de","tid":1235206,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"拉一派打一派有得諗，自由黨嗰啲其實有得拉<br />\n<br />\n搞區，搞到非建制形勢大好，將啲中間派拉過嚟就win win<br />\n<br />\n【勝者全取】香港人有冇本事十八區同時集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234716</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8759cd930230fa1c8c1e5eb1dfd5946a1e985ce","tid":1235206,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"可能會有人問，咁我地揀咩方法呀之後！<br />\n<br />\n雨傘失敗後講咩深耕細作，但最後又無左影<br />\n<br />\n但今次反送中，我們要強調「原則先於方法」<br />\n<br />\n武林門派眾多，但張無忌都識講「萬變不離其宗」<br />\n<br />\n勇武又好，和理非又好，要睇以下心法要點：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">留心</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 睇時機做適當的事情<br />\n<br />\n2. 考慮行動是否合理，是否得到支持<br />\n<br />\n3. 不同意見的人要同情地互相理解<br />\n<br />\n4. 用創意突破框框（個人十分欣賞鳩up巴打的思維）"},{"pid":"59018482822412e4a2f2ce8e0df4ec32e446038b","tid":1235206,"uid":26441,"like